name: Vanilla Sky - Get High
description: This masterwork was created when I was pretty high after smokin' Amnesia Haze. So I was bored at some point and thought: dude, let's create a NFT! Here it is my art piece. It's Cannaboy ridin' a jay straight to Vanilla Sky. Damn, he looks lit. Anyways guys, if you enjoy this art or if this made your day, please help a stoner brother out to finance his next bag of weed with this.
